sequenceDiagram
    participant C as C++ Code (ActivateAbility)
    participant A as Animation (Montage)
    participant E as Event Handler (OnHitEventReceived)

    C->>A: Start Swing (ReadyForActivation)
    C->>C: Setup "Ear" for Hit Tag
    Note over C: ActivateAbility() finishes instantly.
    Note over A: Animation is playing... frame 1... frame 10...
    A->>E: I hit something! (Tag Sent)
    E->>E: Calculate Damage!
    Note over A: Animation finishes...
    A->>C: Animation is Done! (OnCompleted)
    C->>C: EndAbility()
